<synopsis>
int PQsendClosePrepared(PGconn *conn, const char *stmtName);
</synopsis>

       This is an asynchronous version of <xref linkend="libpq-PQclosePrepared"/>:
       it returns 1 if it was able to dispatch the request, and 0 if not.
       After a successful call, call <xref linkend="libpq-PQgetResult"/> to
       obtain the results.  The function's parameters are handled
       identically to <xref linkend="libpq-PQclosePrepared"/>.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
       提交请求以关闭指定的预处理语句，而无需等待完成。
<synopsis>
int PQsendClosePrepared(PGconn *conn, const char *stmtName);
</synopsis>

       这是<xref linkend="libpq-PQclosePrepared"/>的异步版本：
       如果能够发送请求，则返回1，否则返回0。
       成功调用后，调用<xref linkend="libpq-PQgetResult"/>以获取结果。
       该函数的参数处理方式与<xref linkend="libpq-PQclosePrepared"/>相同。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=c432b520934694040cd43f34d95d230f -->
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="libpq-PQsendClosePortal">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=6855e2c2ed46d888c99df34150894804 sig_cn_org=6855e2c2ed46d888c99df34150894804 source=17.5 
     <term><function>PQsendClosePortal</function><indexterm><primary>PQsendClosePortal</primary></indexterm></term>
________________________________________________________-->
     <term><function>PQsendClosePortal</function><indexterm><primary>PQsendClosePortal</primary></indexterm></term>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=6855e2c2ed46d888c99df34150894804 -->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=1a1042d4674de306de775d6f88893e60 sig_cn_org=5d96cfe1a4fcd9951715d9e94d7afc89 source=17.5 
      <para>
       Submits a request to close specified portal, without waiting for
       completion.
<synopsis>
int PQsendClosePortal(PGconn *conn, const char *portalName);
</synopsis>

       This is an asynchronous version of <xref linkend="libpq-PQclosePortal"/>:
       it returns 1 if it was able to dispatch the request, and 0 if not.
       After a successful call, call <xref linkend="libpq-PQgetResult"/> to
       obtain the results.  The function's parameters are handled
       identically to <xref linkend="libpq-PQclosePortal"/>.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
       提交请求以关闭指定的门户，而无需等待完成。
<synopsis>
int PQsendClosePortal(PGconn *conn, const char *portalName);
</synopsis>

       这是<xref linkend="libpq-PQclosePortal"/>的异步版本：
       如果能够发送请求，则返回1，否则返回0。
       成功调用后，调用<xref linkend="libpq-PQgetResult"/>以获取结果。
       该函数的参数处理方式与<xref linkend="libpq-PQclosePortal"/>相同。
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=1a1042d4674de306de775d6f88893e60 -->
